line_1: Sleepy charms I come to break:

line_1: With records thy life's great story;
line_2: Full of triumphs, full of glory.

line_1: One by one thy deeds review,

line_1: Wet with gore, with slaughter stain'd!

line_2: Is to trace his actions past,
